267
00:17:26,505 --> 00:17:38,725
[radio newsreader] I can also tell you
that a multi-agency response is being coordinated, involving… [newsreader 1] The kidnappers have threatened to execute him, with the authorities no closer to identifying his location.

268
00:17:39,768 --> 00:17:42,396
The number of views of the video
