Otherwise, what good am I?

285
00:18:52,382 --> 00:18:55,886
Oh, um, I will clean that up. I promise.
Just don't let anyone touch it.

286
00:19:17,783 --> 00:19:18,992
Ma'am.

287
00:19:19,076 --> 00:19:22,788
