337
00:21:58,527 --> 00:22:03,156
- -Fucking... -[Derek] We don't. Now, it might be…
- -Fucking... -[Derek] We don't. Now, it might be… [Moe] You know you can't say a word about this once it's done, yeah?

338
00:22:04,074 --> 00:22:06,326
