358
00:23:31,912 --> 00:23:41,004
- I'll do it then, shall I?
- [Derek] But it is quite usual in terror-related incidents for the authorities to refrain from sharing information which they think might jeopardize the…

359
00:23:42,047 --> 00:23:44,049
